Reasoning: The paper deals with space-time block codes (STBCs) in a cooperative communication setting, specifically in a partially-coherent relay channel (PCRC). This involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SY), networked systems (cs.NI), and multiple antennas (cs.MM).
